    "body": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p1\" class=\"stimulus_reference \">\n        <div class=\"standalone_image \">\n          <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"The figure presents triangle P Q R, where side P R is horizontal, and point Q is directly above point P. Angle P is a right angle. Angle R is labeled 30 degrees and side Q R is labeled 8.\" width=\"99\" height=\"63\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n",
    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the right triangle shown above, what is the length of&nbsp;<span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"line P Q\"></span></span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
